snippet.title: The Shark Karshon Cast In Aquaman 2 - Deny Biology (Indya Moore) & Support An Abuser (Amber Heard)
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 wants to be an Eco-Friendly messaging movie with a domestic abuser of men & women on the cast and now a transgender non-binary Shark person on the cast?

One half a step forward for the DCEU and then 1,000 footsteps back.

Read more about this story here: https://boundingintocomics.com/2021/10/05/transgender-actor-indya-moore-cast-as-aquatic-green-lantern-villain-in-aquaman-and-the-lost-kingdom/
